title: State of Delaware refers fake BlackRock XRP Trust filing to Department of Justice
description:
The State of Delaware has initiated action against a fraudulent XRP exchange-traded fund (ETF) filing it received, according to reports from Bloomberg on Nov. 14. On Nov. 13, BlackRock appeared to submit a registration to Delware’s Division of Corporations, indicating it is pursuing an XRP exchange-traded fund (ETF).
